{
  "message": "fuzz(alloc-bitmap): add 14 structured corpus seeds\n\nCoverage expansion for fuzz_alloc_bitmap harness:\n- Empty/zero-length bitmaps\n- Single byte bitmaps (all zeros, all ones)\n- Contiguous free runs in middle of bitmap\n- Large index beyond bitmap bounds\n- Wraparound search (start=count, start in last free region)\n- len=0 edge case (returns Some(0))\n- len>count edge case (returns None)\n- Maximum bitmap size (128 bytes)\n- Single free bit with wraparound search\n- Exact byte boundary index access\n- count=0 edge case\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
